data.description: Here is your chance to have a beautiful true five bedroom home situated on a beautiful corner lot!! This home offers so much space. Your master bedroom will give you a large sitting area, open windows for all your natural lighting, a large bathroom with double vanities, garden tub, stand alone shower, and a large walk in closet, plus is on the first floor! All your secondary rooms will be upstairs with the large open flex area. If your looking for space and a perfect floorplan, this is your home! The bedrooms also have huge closets. The kitchen offers a large elegant island, cabinets galore, and open to the living area.  Take a look today!
